{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":870,"text":"June 29, 2016."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7150,"text":"My dear fellow citizen:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":10775,"text":"I write to you today,"},{"time":14393,"text":"to you who have lost in this era."},{"time":19708,"text":"At this moment in our common life,"},{"time":23950,"text":"when the world is full of breaking"},{"time":26425,"text":"and spite"},{"time":28239,"text":"and fear,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31385,"text":"I address this letter"},{"time":33863,"text":"simply to you,"},{"time":36494,"text":"even though we both know"},{"time":38086,"text":"there are many of you behind this \"you,\""},{"time":43306,"text":"and many of me behind this \"I.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":50525,"text":"I write to you because at present,"},{"time":54478,"text":"this quaking world we share scares me."},{"time":60819,"text":"I gather it scares you, too."},{"time":64618,"text":"Some of what we fear, I suspect,"},{"time":67671,"text":"we fear in common."},{"time":70169,"text":"But much of what we fear\nseems to be each other."},{"time":76736,"text":"You fear the world I want to live in,"},{"time":80529,"text":"and I fear your visions in turn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85673,"text":"Do you know that feeling you get\nwhen you know it's going to storm"},{"time":90470,"text":"before it storms?"},{"time":94001,"text":"Do you also feel that now,"},{"time":97276,"text":"fellow citizen?"},{"time":100435,"text":"That malaise and worry"},{"time":104181,"text":"that some who know"},{"time":107517,"text":"feel reminds them of the 1930s?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111878,"text":"Perhaps you don't,"},{"time":114493,"text":"because our fears of each other"},{"time":116424,"text":"are not in sync."},{"time":119325,"text":"In this round, I sense\nthat your fears of me,"},{"time":123655,"text":"of the world that I have insisted\nis right for us both,"},{"time":128856,"text":"has gathered over a generation."},{"time":132017,"text":"It took time for your fears\nto trigger my fears,"},{"time":136868,"text":"not least because at first,"},{"time":139666,"text":"I never thought I needed to fear you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144882,"text":"I heard you"},{"time":147737,"text":"but did not listen,"},{"time":149731,"text":"all these years when you said\nthat this amazing new world"},{"time":156204,"text":"wasn't amazing for you,"},{"time":158879,"text":"for many of you,"},{"time":160507,"text":"across the industrialized world;"},{"time":163918,"text":"that the open, liquid world I relished,"},{"time":166763,"text":"of people and goods\nand technologies flowing freely,"},{"time":171090,"text":"going where they pleased, globally,"},{"time":175019,"text":"was not, for you, an emancipation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181453,"text":"I have walked through your towns"},{"time":185442,"text":"and, while looking, failed to see."},{"time":190799,"text":"I did notice in Stephenville, Texas,"},{"time":195791,"text":"that the town square was dominated"},{"time":198122,"text":"by one lawyer's office after another,"},{"time":202394,"text":"because of all the people\nrotating in and out of the prison."},{"time":206224,"text":"I did notice the barren shops\nin Wagner, South Dakota,"},{"time":211925,"text":"and the VFW gathering hall"},{"time":216314,"text":"that stood in mockery"},{"time":218934,"text":"of a community's dream to endure."},{"time":223352,"text":"I did notice"},{"time":225323,"text":"at the Lancaster, Pennsylvania Wal-Mart,"},{"time":229445,"text":"that far too many people\nin their 20s and 30s"},{"time":233828,"text":"looked a decade or two from death,"},{"time":237295,"text":"with patchy, flared-up skin"},{"time":239665,"text":"and thinning, stringy hair"},{"time":242165,"text":"and browning, ground-down teeth"},{"time":243841,"text":"and a lostness in their eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248160,"text":"I did notice that the young people\nI encountered in Paris,"},{"time":252794,"text":"in Florence, in Barcelona,"},{"time":254769,"text":"had degrees but no place to take them,"},{"time":259712,"text":"living on internships well into their 30s,"},{"time":263693,"text":"their lives prevented from launching,"},{"time":267868,"text":"because of an economy\nthat creates wealth --"},{"time":271409,"text":"just not jobs."},{"time":273836,"text":"I did notice the news about those parts\nof London becoming ghost quarters,"},{"time":281025,"text":"where the global super-rich\nturn fishy money into empty apartments"},{"time":287962,"text":"and price lifelong residents of a city,\nyoung couples starting out,"},{"time":292088,"text":"out of their own home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296332,"text":"And I heard that the fabric of your life"},{"time":299277,"text":"was tearing."},{"time":301574,"text":"You used to be able to count on work,"},{"time":304840,"text":"and now you couldn't."},{"time":306977,"text":"You used to be able\nto nourish your children,"},{"time":311079,"text":"and guarantee that they would climb"},{"time":314052,"text":"a little bit further in life than you had,"},{"time":318002,"text":"and now you couldn't."},{"time":320374,"text":"You used to be made to feel dignity\nin your work, and now you didn't."},{"time":327795,"text":"It used to be normal\nfor people like you to own a home,"},{"time":332470,"text":"and now it wasn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335286,"text":"I cannot say"},{"time":338426,"text":"I didn't know these things,"},{"time":341701,"text":"but I was distracted"},{"time":345569,"text":"creating a future in which\nwe could live on Mars,"},{"time":351091,"text":"even as you struggled down here on Earth."},{"time":356155,"text":"I was distracted"},{"time":358455,"text":"innovating immortality,"},{"time":362519,"text":"even as many of you began to live\nshorter lives than your parents had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369301,"text":"I heard all of these things,\nbut I didn't listen."},{"time":373528,"text":"I looked"},{"time":375566,"text":"but didn't see."},{"time":377161,"text":"I read, didn't understand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381370,"text":"I paid attention"},{"time":383389,"text":"only when you began to vote and shout,"},{"time":388428,"text":"and when your voting and shouting,\nwhen the substance of it,"},{"time":391516,"text":"began to threaten me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396235,"text":"I listened only when you moved\ntoward shattering continental unions"},{"time":401252,"text":"and electing vulgar demagogues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404704,"text":"Only then did your pain become of interest"},{"time":409343,"text":"to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412317,"text":"I know that feeling hurt"},{"time":414295,"text":"is often prologue to dealing hurt."},{"time":419664,"text":"I wonder now"},{"time":422408,"text":"if you would be less eager to deal it"},{"time":425438,"text":"if I had stood with you"},{"time":427402,"text":"when you merely felt it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431313,"text":"I ask myself"},{"time":433355,"text":"why I didn't stand with you then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436874,"text":"One reason is that I became entranced"},{"time":440275,"text":"by the gurus of change,"},{"time":443187,"text":"became a worshiper of the religion\nof the new for novelty's sake,"},{"time":447546,"text":"and of globalization and open borders"},{"time":449723,"text":"and kaleidoscopic diversity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454928,"text":"Once change became my totalizing faith,"},{"time":460415,"text":"I could be blind."},{"time":463143,"text":"I could fail to see change's consequences."},{"time":467866,"text":"I could overlook the importance"},{"time":469827,"text":"of roots, traditions,\nrituals, stability --"},{"time":472953,"text":"and belonging."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475501,"text":"And the more fundamentalist I became"},{"time":478840,"text":"in my worship of change and openness,"},{"time":484090,"text":"the more I drove you\ntowards the other polarity,"},{"time":488074,"text":"to cling,"},{"time":489632,"text":"to freeze,"},{"time":491277,"text":"to close,"},{"time":493100,"text":"to belong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496138,"text":"I now see as I didn't before"},{"time":498878,"text":"that not having\nthe right skin or right organ"},{"time":502843,"text":"is not the only varietal of disadvantage."},{"time":507722,"text":"There is a subtler, quieter disadvantage"},{"time":511336,"text":"in having those privileged traits"},{"time":514675,"text":"and yet feeling history to be\nmoving away from you;"},{"time":519082,"text":"that while the past was hospitable\nto people like you,"},{"time":522499,"text":"the future will be more hospitable"},{"time":524921,"text":"to others;"},{"time":526338,"text":"that the world is growing less familiar,"},{"time":528815,"text":"less yours day by day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533865,"text":"I will not concede for a moment\nthat old privileges should not dwindle."},{"time":540055,"text":"They cannot dwindle fast enough."},{"time":543785,"text":"It is for you to learn to live\nin a new century in which"},{"time":547310,"text":"there are no bonuses for showing up\nwith the right skin and right organs."},{"time":553277,"text":"If and when your anger turns to hate,"},{"time":555729,"text":"please know that there is no space\nfor that in our shared home."},{"time":561642,"text":"But I will admit, fellow citizen,"},{"time":566140,"text":"that I have discounted the burden\nof coping with the loss of status."},{"time":572163,"text":"I have forgotten"},{"time":573957,"text":"that what is socially necessary\ncan also be personally gruelling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":580919,"text":"A similar thing happened"},{"time":583217,"text":"with the economy that you and I share."},{"time":588191,"text":"Just as I cannot and don't wish"},{"time":590647,"text":"to turn back to the clock\non equality and diversity,"},{"time":594298,"text":"and yet must understand"},{"time":596651,"text":"the sense of loss they can inspire,"},{"time":601027,"text":"so, too, I refuse\nand could not if I wished"},{"time":605970,"text":"turn back the clock on an ever more\nclosely knit, interdependent world,"},{"time":610135,"text":"and on inventions\nthat won't stop being invented."},{"time":614520,"text":"And yet I must understand\nyour experience of these things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621032,"text":"You have for years been telling me\nthat your experience of these things"},{"time":624475,"text":"is not as good as my theories forecast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628528,"text":"Yet before you could finish\na complaining sentence"},{"time":634116,"text":"about the difficulty of living\nwith erratic hours, volatile pay,"},{"time":639628,"text":"vanishing opportunities,"},{"time":641278,"text":"about the pain of dropping\nyour children off at 24-hour day care"},{"time":645560,"text":"to make your 3am shift,"},{"time":648319,"text":"I shot back at you -- before you\ncould finish your sentence --"},{"time":652256,"text":"my dogma,"},{"time":653622,"text":"about how what you are actually\nexperiencing was flexibility"},{"time":658794,"text":"and freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662591,"text":"Language is one of the only things\nthat we truly share,"},{"time":668549,"text":"and I sometimes used\nthis joint inheritance"},{"time":672052,"text":"to obfuscate"},{"time":673821,"text":"and deflect"},{"time":675479,"text":"and justify myself;"},{"time":677933,"text":"to re-brand what was good for me"},{"time":679837,"text":"as something appearing good for us both,"},{"time":683324,"text":"when I threw around terms\nlike \"the sharing economy,\""},{"time":688135,"text":"and \"disruption\""},{"time":689845,"text":"and \"global resourcing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":693224,"text":"I see now that what I was really doing,"},{"time":696229,"text":"at times,"},{"time":697894,"text":"was buying your pain on the cheap,"},{"time":701892,"text":"sprucing it up"},{"time":703772,"text":"and trying to sell it back to you"},{"time":706244,"text":"as freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709712,"text":"I have wanted to believe\nand wanted you to believe"},{"time":715683,"text":"that the system that has been good to me,"},{"time":717816,"text":"that has made my life ever more seamless,"},{"time":721229,"text":"is also the best system for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725544,"text":"I have condescended to you"},{"time":727829,"text":"with the idea that you are voting\nagainst your economic interests --"},{"time":732207,"text":"voting against your interests,"},{"time":735621,"text":"as if I know your interests."},{"time":740296,"text":"That is just my dogmatic\neconomism talking."},{"time":745723,"text":"I have a weakness"},{"time":747524,"text":"for treating people's economic interests\nas their only interest,"},{"time":752933,"text":"ignoring things like belonging and pride"},{"time":756481,"text":"and the desire to send a message\nto those who ignore you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":760688,"text":"So here we are,"},{"time":764243,"text":"in a scary but not inexplicable moment"},{"time":769507,"text":"of demagoguery, fracture,"},{"time":772481,"text":"xenophobia, resentment and fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777628,"text":"And I worry for us both\nif we continue down this road,"},{"time":782358,"text":"me not listening,"},{"time":784305,"text":"you feeling unheard,"},{"time":786180,"text":"you shouting to get me to listen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":790779,"text":"I worry when each of us is seduced\nby visions of the future"},{"time":794254,"text":"that have no place for the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797731,"text":"If this goes on,"},{"time":801655,"text":"if this goes on,"},{"time":804053,"text":"there may be blood."},{"time":807290,"text":"There are already hints of this blood"},{"time":810915,"text":"in newspapers every day."},{"time":812967,"text":"There may be roundups, raids,"},{"time":815586,"text":"deportations, camps, secessions."},{"time":819494,"text":"And no, I do not think that I exaggerate."},{"time":824236,"text":"There may be even talk of war"},{"time":826181,"text":"in places that were certain\nthey were done with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831483,"text":"There is always the hope of redemption."},{"time":835764,"text":"But it will not be a cheap,\nshallow redemption"},{"time":839066,"text":"that comes through blather\nabout us all being in it together."},{"time":843312,"text":"This will take more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846396,"text":"It will take accepting that we both\nmade choices to be here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853863,"text":"We create our \"others.\""},{"time":857975,"text":"As parents, as neighbors, as citizens,"},{"time":862503,"text":"we witness and sometimes ignore each other"},{"time":866858,"text":"into being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":869268,"text":"You were not born vengeful."},{"time":873339,"text":"I have some role"},{"time":875370,"text":"in whatever thirst\nyou now feel for revenge,"},{"time":879685,"text":"and that thirst now tempts me"},{"time":881622,"text":"to plot ever more elaborate escapes"},{"time":884164,"text":"from our common life,"},{"time":886107,"text":"from the schools and neighborhoods"},{"time":888000,"text":"and airports and amusement parks"},{"time":889955,"text":"that we used to share."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893659,"text":"We face, then,"},{"time":896671,"text":"a problem not of these large,\nimpersonal forces."},{"time":902366,"text":"We face a problem\nof your and my relations."},{"time":907815,"text":"We chose ways of relating to each other"},{"time":912345,"text":"that got us here."},{"time":913896,"text":"We can choose ways of relating"},{"time":916669,"text":"that get us out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919361,"text":"But there are things\nwe might have to let go of,"},{"time":923418,"text":"fellow citizen,"},{"time":925674,"text":"starting with our own cherished\nversions of reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":933035,"text":"Imagine if you let go of fantasies"},{"time":936928,"text":"of a society purged\nof these or those people."},{"time":941561,"text":"Imagine if I let go of my habit"},{"time":945755,"text":"of saving the world behind your back,"},{"time":949833,"text":"of deliberating on the future"},{"time":951254,"text":"of your work,"},{"time":953260,"text":"your food,"},{"time":954530,"text":"your schools,"},{"time":956024,"text":"in places where you couldn't\nget past security."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960386,"text":"We can do this only if we first accept"},{"time":965347,"text":"that we have neglected each other."},{"time":969971,"text":"If there is hope to summon"},{"time":973930,"text":"in this ominous hour,"},{"time":976202,"text":"it is this."},{"time":978870,"text":"We have, for too long,"},{"time":981547,"text":"chased various shimmering dreams"},{"time":985818,"text":"at the cost of attention\nto the foundational dream of each other,"},{"time":993101,"text":"the dream of tending to each other,"},{"time":995693,"text":"of unleashing each other's wonders,"},{"time":998580,"text":"of moving through history together."},{"time":1002046,"text":"We could dare to commit\nto the dream of each other"},{"time":1007009,"text":"as the thing that matters\nbefore every neon thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012476,"text":"Let us dare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014467,"text":"Sincerely yours,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1016067,"text":"a fellow citizen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017683,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}